1. *Rizik* je postojao da se dogodi nesreća. (The risk existed that an accident would occur.)
2. Oni su podneli *rizike* da bi postigli cilj. (They took the risks in order to achieve the goal.)
3. To je veoma *riziko* situacija. (This is a very risky situation.)
4. Oni su *rizikovali* da bi nam pomogli. (They risked in order to help us.)
5. Svi su bili svesni *rizika* koji im se suočavao. (Everyone was aware of the risks they were facing.)